WEBVTT

00:01.480 --> 00:03.820
♪

00:04.805 --> 00:06.456
<i>CHRISTOS: One plant contains it all.</i>

00:07.531 --> 00:08.737
<i>You really did it.</i>

00:09.240 --> 00:12.233
- <i>It's gonna be a bumper crop.</i>
- Did you hear what I said?

00:13.765 --> 00:15.527
All of our warships are gone, Dad.

00:15.981 --> 00:17.423
We can't go to Malta.

00:19.220 --> 00:20.341
Leningrad.

00:20.748 --> 00:23.798
[SIGHS] We can't go there either.

00:23.980 --> 00:26.840
♪

00:27.459 --> 00:29.079
September 1941.

00:29.179 --> 00:32.519
Hitler's troops lay siege
to Leningrad for 900 days

00:32.619 --> 00:36.043
of the blackest, most wretched
misery in human history.

00:38.470 --> 00:40.110
Do you any idea what happens to your body

00:40.150 --> 00:41.637
when starvation sets in?

00:42.378 --> 00:43.680
It shrinks.

00:45.084 --> 00:47.064
Heart and lungs compress.

00:47.164 --> 00:49.104
Eyes, testicles, ovaries

00:49.204 --> 00:50.784
just shrivel up and wither away.

00:50.884 --> 00:52.918
Your muscles devour themselves.

00:52.975 --> 00:55.155
Temperature falls, you freeze.

00:55.255 --> 00:57.061
Why are you telling me this?

00:58.599 --> 01:01.877
Nikolai Vavilov is why I'm
telling you this, my daughter.

01:01.878 --> 01:03.614
I'm telling you this
because hidden in a bunker

01:03.638 --> 01:06.178
barely 10 feet beneath that monstrous decay

01:06.278 --> 01:10.231
and rot of existence in
Leningrad was salvation, Lucia.

01:11.413 --> 01:15.288
The world's first global
plant bank from Vavilov.

01:16.238 --> 01:19.378
400,000 thousand seeds, roots, vegetables,

01:19.478 --> 01:21.962
protected not by guns

01:22.595 --> 01:24.002
but by science.

01:24.482 --> 01:25.742
By science.

01:26.449 --> 01:29.543
Yet even Vavilov's devoted acolytes

01:29.642 --> 01:31.482
couldn't beat the terror raging above them.

01:31.562 --> 01:32.945
And finally they,

01:33.974 --> 01:36.697
having never even touched one plant

01:37.229 --> 01:39.201
for their own escape from doom,

01:40.469 --> 01:41.881
also starved to death.

01:42.519 --> 01:45.886
I'm telling you this because
you're my little girl,

01:46.567 --> 01:47.903
and I love you.

01:48.533 --> 01:50.073
And where Vavilov failed,

01:50.173 --> 01:52.873
we will succeed in spreading
salvation to the world

01:52.973 --> 01:55.513
for the protection of its
future, to protect your future.

01:55.613 --> 01:58.593
Because right now, from
every point on the globe,

01:58.693 --> 02:00.753
planes are converging on Malta.

02:01.288 --> 02:04.491
And from there, we deliver
our gift to the world.

02:05.422 --> 02:08.913
Our gift to ourselves, Lucia.

02:10.175 --> 02:11.293
[EXHALES SHARPLY]

02:12.213 --> 02:17.033
♪

02:18.779 --> 02:19.975
Where are you going?

02:20.017 --> 02:23.317
♪

02:23.597 --> 02:24.750
Where are you going?

02:25.619 --> 02:28.159
♪

02:28.259 --> 02:31.246
You can't leave me now.
We're so close, son.

02:32.219 --> 02:34.839
♪

02:35.250 --> 02:37.159
Please don't go.

02:37.259 --> 02:38.839
♪

02:39.562 --> 02:41.177
[WHISPERS] Don't go.

02:42.339 --> 02:45.759
♪

02:46.322 --> 02:49.987
There are active ports
in Syracuse and Tripoli.

02:50.638 --> 02:53.540
Benghazi, if he's got the fuel.

02:53.798 --> 02:55.125
Vellek's not a runner.

02:55.165 --> 02:57.021
The Greek convoy's rusting
at the bottom of the Med.

02:57.045 --> 02:58.465
He can't stay put either.

02:58.565 --> 03:00.261
With a helo, he can get at
least some of his product

03:00.285 --> 03:02.195
to just about anywhere in this area.

03:02.243 --> 03:03.463
If it's planes he's meeting,

03:03.563 --> 03:04.883
we'll need to focus on airfields.

03:04.923 --> 03:06.743
- [KNOCK ON DOOR]
- Come in.

03:07.274 --> 03:09.244
We have a navy blue from Commander Garnett.

03:09.338 --> 03:10.398
[DOOR CLOSES]

03:10.914 --> 03:15.094
