03:16.142 --> 03:18.106
- That crazy son of a bitch.
- SASHA: What?

03:18.298 --> 03:20.195
Haifa Aegis Ashore picked
up three planes inbound,

03:20.219 --> 03:22.176
headed for an airfield in Mdina.

03:22.551 --> 03:23.860
Malta.

03:24.704 --> 03:28.208
He knows we're coming for him,
and he's still going to Malta.

