I, uh, pulled it off the RHIB.

04:34.246 --> 04:36.108
Didn't want to let it go to waste.

04:37.495 --> 04:38.581
[EXHALES]

04:38.990 --> 04:46.709
♪

04:47.410 --> 04:48.782
[CLEARS THROAT]

04:50.080 --> 04:52.740
Ever notice how all the women
here have names that end in "A"?

04:53.225 --> 04:54.230
What?

04:54.269 --> 04:57.160
Kara, Alisha, Sasha, Azima.

04:57.185 --> 04:59.041
- BURK: Andrea.
- MILLER: Commander Garnett. There you go.

04:59.065 --> 05:01.405
So what? So don't you think
that's a little strange?

05:02.045 --> 05:04.650
I think that all of you
are a little strange.

05:05.178 --> 05:07.805
All right, lock it up.
Captain's got the floor.

05:08.389 --> 05:10.054
Listen up. We don't have much time.

05:10.349 --> 05:12.569
Here's the plan... you're
gonna RHIB to Malta,

05:12.669 --> 05:13.849
landing in Valletta

05:13.949 --> 05:15.854
and approaching from the southwest.

05:16.931 --> 05:19.191
The airstrip is 12 klicks inland,

05:19.292 --> 05:21.052
so you're gonna need
to find ground mobility.

05:22.157 --> 05:24.457
Vellek knows we're on his
ass, so he's gonna work fast.

05:24.612 --> 05:27.032
We don't know exactly how
he's gonna deliver his product,

05:27.132 --> 05:29.392
but it's gonna be packed
for a quick hand-off.

05:29.492 --> 05:31.388
JETER: We estimate the
planes will beat you to Malta

05:31.412 --> 05:32.832
by about 10 minutes.

05:32.932 --> 05:34.828
They'll most likely be
loaded and ready for takeoff

05:34.852 --> 05:36.153
by the time you land.

05:36.612 --> 05:38.452
SLATTERY: Meantime,
<i>Nathan James</i> will continue

05:38.532 --> 05:39.772
the search for Vellek's ship,

05:39.852 --> 05:41.372
But your job is to keep those planes

05:41.452 --> 05:43.512
from taking off with the package.

05:44.753 --> 05:47.159
You understand, you cannot
let those planes get airborne,

05:47.418 --> 05:48.523
at any cost.

05:49.562 --> 05:52.143
- [SPEAKS MALTESE] _
- [AZIMA SPEAKS ITALIAN] _

05:52.144 --> 05:54.124
SLATTERY: We've all seen
what this drug can do...

05:54.498 --> 05:56.058
some of us firsthand.

05:56.082 --> 05:59.097
If Vellek's Nostos-laced
"cure" gets out into the world,

05:59.480 --> 06:01.907
there won't be much
humanity left to fight for.

06:02.007 --> 06:04.199
- [SPEAKING ITALIAN] _
- _

