06:29.381 --> 06:30.882
DANNY: <i>Nathan James</i>, Vulture is in.

06:30.883 --> 06:33.789
<i>Helo just took off. We are
now in position on the tarmac.</i>

06:34.448 --> 06:36.370
<i>I can confirm visuals on two planes.</i>

06:36.401 --> 06:38.761
Three hostiles loading crates.
British and Russian crews.

06:38.841 --> 06:40.661
Roger, Vulture. Don't start blowing shit up

06:40.761 --> 06:42.370
till we know what's in those crates.

06:42.620 --> 06:44.340
<i>We still need those progenitor seeds.</i>

06:44.420 --> 06:46.240
Copy. Vulture, on me.

06:46.265 --> 06:47.282
All right.

06:47.500 --> 06:50.960
[INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS]

06:51.060 --> 06:55.400
