08:24.448 --> 08:25.828
- [GUNFIRE]
- Status unknown!

08:25.928 --> 08:27.848
<i>We are taking sniper fire from the tower!</i>

08:27.928 --> 08:29.428
Divert from search pattern.

08:29.528 --> 08:31.548
- Set course for Malta. Flank speed.
- Aye, sir.

08:32.025 --> 08:34.400
- Any other ships in the area?
- Showing five unidentified vessels.

08:34.424 --> 08:35.846
No distinctive signatures.

08:36.275 --> 08:37.936
The Americans found the airfield.

08:38.035 --> 08:40.936
