09:01.253 --> 09:02.550
Christos!

09:05.086 --> 09:06.228
Christos.

09:06.746 --> 09:07.935
Christos.

09:08.658 --> 09:09.772
Look, you gotta...

09:10.882 --> 09:12.258
Aw, man.

09:13.334 --> 09:15.394
Stop it, man. Stop disappearing on me.

09:15.495 --> 09:17.292
I need you here. Here! Here!

09:18.839 --> 09:20.386
<i>We need to finish what we started.</i>

09:20.443 --> 09:22.703
I know. I know. I know. I will.

09:22.803 --> 09:24.783
I will. I know we're
close. I know we're just...

09:24.883 --> 09:26.103
we're just so close.

09:26.880 --> 09:27.903
[SIGHS]

09:28.311 --> 09:29.416
Come on.

09:29.803 --> 09:30.803
