- On three!

10:02.172 --> 10:03.548
- One! Two!
- I swear to God, Danny!

10:03.572 --> 10:06.102
- Three!
- God! Damn it!

10:06.564 --> 10:07.709
[DANNY SHOUTS]

10:07.911 --> 10:10.650
[GUNFIRE]

10:11.587 --> 10:12.845
Let's go! Let's go!

10:12.870 --> 10:14.806
♪

10:14.831 --> 10:16.952
- Aah!
- [TIRES SCREECH]

10:19.791 --> 10:23.353
[GUNFIRE CONTINUES]

10:24.950 --> 10:25.930
Come on!

10:25.959 --> 10:27.619
[GUNFIRE CONTINUES]

10:27.875 --> 10:29.527
[GRUNTING]

10:29.606 --> 10:31.739
- Aah!
- Green!

10:31.852 --> 10:32.912
[GUNFIRE CONTINUES]

10:33.012 --> 10:36.752
[INDISTINCT SHOUTING]

10:36.852 --> 10:40.752
- [GUNFIRE]
- [GRUNTS]

10:40.852 --> 10:43.072
- [GUNFIRE CONTINUES]
- Aah!

10:43.172 --> 10:45.832
♪

10:45.932 --> 10:47.512
[GRUNTING]

10:47.612 --> 10:51.112
[GUNFIRE CONTINUES]

10:51.696 --> 10:52.974
Aah!

10:54.509 --> 10:55.849
No, no, take Miller first!

10:55.949 --> 10:57.589
- You lost your voting rights, man!
- Aah!

10:58.172 --> 11:01.085
[GUNFIRE]

11:01.086 --> 11:03.067
Aah! Aah!

11:04.444 --> 11:05.974
Keep looking for the seeds!

11:06.604 --> 11:10.413
[GUNFIRE CONTINUES, INDISTINCT SHOUTING]

11:11.564 --> 11:13.024
[GUNFIRE CONTINUES]

11:13.124 --> 11:14.579
[GRUNTING]

11:15.284 --> 11:16.953
[GUNFIRE CONTINUES]

11:16.954 --> 11:17.974
[GRUNTING]

11:18.074 --> 11:21.014
[GUNFIRE CONTINUES]

11:21.114 --> 11:22.174
[GUNFIRE CONTINUES]

11:22.274 --> 11:24.174
[GRUNTING]

11:25.603 --> 11:26.680
Be advised,

11:26.681 --> 11:29.301
<i>sniper is neutralized, but
we're still taking fire.</i>

11:29.401 --> 11:31.381
Miller and Green are secure, but down hard.

11:31.481 --> 11:33.532
<i>We need to get them exfil, ASAP!</i>

11:33.611 --> 11:35.158
Do you have the seeds?

11:35.331 --> 11:37.591
<i>AZIMA: Negative. No sign of the progenitor.</i>

11:37.691 --> 11:40.751
