11:54.437 --> 11:56.737
<i>I say again, the bugs are
the vector for the Nostos.</i>

11:56.837 --> 11:58.937
<i>You need to destroy those crates.</i>

11:59.037 --> 12:01.577
[GUNFIRE]

12:01.677 --> 12:04.851
<i>Don't let any bugs get off that plane!
They all must burn!</i>

12:05.741 --> 12:08.481
