- I know.

13:03.953 --> 13:05.296
Come on, come on.

13:05.953 --> 13:07.773
Hey, hey, hey, hey. Stay with me.

13:07.873 --> 13:10.093
It's okay. Come on. This ain't nothin'.

13:10.773 --> 13:12.118
This ain't nothin', right?

13:12.119 --> 13:13.539
- Come on, Miller.
- [GRUNTS]

13:13.639 --> 13:17.200
[PROPELLERS WHIRRING]

13:17.959 --> 13:19.379
♪

13:19.891 --> 13:21.151
You gotta be kidding me.

13:21.251 --> 13:22.471
- [GUNFIRE]
- Uhh!

13:22.571 --> 13:25.071
- There's a third plane!
- [GUNFIRE]

13:25.171 --> 13:27.881
<i>I say again, a third
plane on the north runway!</i>

13:28.090 --> 13:30.908
- <i>I do not have a line to take target.</i>
- [RADIO CLICKS]

13:31.330 --> 13:33.070
[ENGINE RUMBLING]

13:33.170 --> 13:36.030
- Go.
- No.

13:36.494 --> 13:39.099
