19:05.847 --> 19:09.607
♪

19:12.695 --> 19:13.831
They're rounding the island for cover.

19:13.855 --> 19:15.035
Okay, all ahead full.

19:15.135 --> 19:16.515
Negative. I'm going to slow down.

19:16.615 --> 19:17.791
I want to see what's around that turn.

19:17.815 --> 19:19.155
All ahead, 2/3.

19:19.255 --> 19:20.395
[MAN SPEAKS GREEK]

19:20.495 --> 19:23.195
♪

19:23.534 --> 19:25.303
Vellek's props are decreasing speed.

19:26.174 --> 19:28.834
Slower is good. Hooking a
ship at night's hard enough.

19:28.934 --> 19:30.824
Don't want to try it at 30 knots.

19:32.608 --> 19:34.948
Crossing the interception
point. Zodiac is there.

19:35.049 --> 19:36.789
[INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS]

19:37.426 --> 19:38.508
Good luck.

19:38.609 --> 19:43.269
