26:02.318 --> 26:03.490
Christos.

26:03.638 --> 26:05.425
[SIGHS] They're coming for us.

26:05.919 --> 26:07.436
We have to leave, son.

26:08.438 --> 26:10.138
[DING]

26:10.494 --> 26:12.754
Christos? We gotta go, man. Where are you?

26:12.779 --> 26:13.972
<i>Right here, Dad.</i>

26:14.414 --> 26:21.404
♪

26:24.014 --> 26:28.954
♪

26:30.071 --> 26:31.544
The seeds. Where are they?

26:31.993 --> 26:33.050
My son...

26:33.273 --> 26:34.471
It's over, Vellek,

26:34.943 --> 26:36.303
but you can still redeem yourself.

26:36.383 --> 26:38.027
You can redeem your family.

26:38.343 --> 26:40.603
Give us the formula for
the cure without the Nostos.

26:40.703 --> 26:41.982
Feed the world.

26:45.122 --> 26:47.107
A random act of violence.

26:49.523 --> 26:52.259
That's what they called it
when my son was beaten to death.

26:53.362 --> 26:55.822
Then the virus came, and
"random" became "constant."

26:55.922 --> 26:57.942
Man's real nature, his conscience,

26:58.042 --> 27:00.013
his compassion, went to sleep.

27:01.461 --> 27:03.642
Smothered by his addiction to violence.

27:04.624 --> 27:05.960
I offered a way back.

27:06.061 --> 27:08.037
It wasn't a way back. It was a way out.

27:08.626 --> 27:10.961
You have a formula. You have the seeds.

27:11.525 --> 27:13.486
- Whatever you've done...
- Cannot be undone.

27:13.941 --> 27:21.161
♪

27:21.953 --> 27:23.320
What's gone is gone.

27:23.421 --> 27:29.881
♪

27:30.790 --> 27:32.841
