from one hell of a fight.

29:06.955 --> 29:08.255
But we're not done here.

29:08.355 --> 29:10.615
<i>Our Captain needs volunteers to join him</i>

29:10.715 --> 29:12.555
<i>in boarding the enemy
ship and bringing Cooper,</i>

29:12.595 --> 29:14.815
Captain Chandler, and those
seeds back in one piece.

29:14.915 --> 29:16.715
Anyone willing to lay
their lives on the line,

29:16.795 --> 29:19.375
muster in the Helo bay in five minutes.

29:20.242 --> 29:21.375
That is all.

29:22.555 --> 29:28.095
